    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1942-01-25T22:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1942-01-25T22:00:00-05:00" n="237"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d237">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">701.0010/17c: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Argentina</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Armour</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1942-01-25T22:00:00-05:00"
                            >January 25, 1942—10 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>109. For your information the following message is being sent to our missions in
                    Lima, Santiago, Montevideo, Rio, Quito, La Paz, Asunción.</p>
                <quote rend="blockquote">
                    <p>“In anticipation of an early break in diplomatic relations with the Axis on
                        the part of the country to which you are accredited, you may, in your
                        discretion, suggest to the appropriate authorities the desirability of
                        taking suitable measures to prevent the departure of Axis diplomats and
                        officials and particularly of unofficial agents especially to such other
                        American republic or republics as may not be expected to sever relations in
                        the immediate future. A concentration of these officials and agents is
                        obviously undesirable.”</p>
                </quote>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
